'''Saint John Energy''', formerly known as '''Power Commission of the City of Saint John''' and '''Civic Hydro''', is the electrical utility reseller of power purchased from [[NB Power]] in [[Saint John, New Brunswick]]. It was founded in 1922 and now serves over 36,000 customers.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.sjenergy.com/uploads/file/annual_reports/annual_report_2013_corporate.pdf |title=Saint John Energy Annual Report 2013 |accessdate=2015-01-08}}</ref>
The utility sells 950GWh of electricity annually, however the utility has no electrical generating capacity of its own.
